- total 52 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-022: CLI publish 命令 — Design Document\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Diagram\n```\n┌─────────────────┐\n│  CLI Interface  │\n│  (publish.py)   │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n┌────────▼────────┐\n│  Auth Manager   │\n│   (auth.py)     │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n┌────────▼────────┐\n│ Registry Client │\n│ (registry.py)   │\n└────────┬────────┘","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/design.md","time":{"start":1775894257867,"end":1775894257887}}}}
