{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894354765,"sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8c6913001PJBh3zoW03ad38","messageID":"msg_d7b8c2a50001BFxiORKBoKqeCK","sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:11","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","content":"# AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Design Document\n\n## Architecture\n\n### Component Diagram\n```\n┌─────────────────┐\n│   CLI Commands  │\n│  (deploy, etc)  │\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n┌────────▼────────┐\n│  DockerService  │\n│ (docker_service)│\n└────────┬────────┘\n         │\n    ┌────┴────┐\n    ▼         ▼\n┌───────┐ ┌───────┐\n│Docker │ │Docker │\n│ SDK   │ │ CLI   │\n└───┬───┘ └───────┘\n    │\n    ▼\n┌─────────┐\n│ Docker  │\n│ Daemon  │\n└─────────┘\n```\n\n## Key Design Decisions\n\n### Dual Backend Strategy\n- Primary: Docker SDK for Python (docker-py)\n- Fallback: Docker CLI subprocess calls\n- Automatic detection of available backend\n\n### Connection Management\n- Support for local Docker socket (unix:///var/run/docker.sock)\n- Support for remote Docker daemon via env variables\n- Connection pooling for SDK backend\n\n### Error Handling\n- Custom exception hierarchy for Docker-specific errors\n- Structured error messages with actionable suggestions\n- Retry logic for transient failures\n\n### Async Support\n- Async methods for long-running operations (pull, build)\n- Callback-based progress reporting\n- Timeout configuration per operation\n\n## Data Flow\n1. CLI command calls DockerService method\n2. Service validates parameters\n3. Execute via SDK or CLI backend\n4. Parse and structure response\n5. Return result or raise exception\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/design.md","time":{"start":1775894354736,"end":1775894354764}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894354767,"sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8c997e001R7SKzpJyx077AK","messageID":"msg_d7b8c2a50001BFxiORKBoKqeCK","sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:12","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/plan.md","content":"# AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Implementation Plan\n\n## Phase 1: Foundation\n- [ ] Create DockerService class structure\n- [ ] Define exception hierarchy\n- [ ] Implement configuration management\n- [ ] Set up backend detection logic\n\n## Phase 2: Container Operations\n- [ ] Implement container creation\n- [ ] Implement container start/stop/restart\n- [ ] Implement container removal\n- [ ] Implement container inspection\n- [ ] Implement container listing\n\n## Phase 3: Image Operations\n- [ ] Implement image pulling\n- [ ] Implement image building\n- [ ] Implement image listing\n- [ ] Implement image removal\n- [ ] Add progress callbacks\n\n## Phase 4: Network & Volume\n- [ ] Implement network creation\n- [ ] Implement network listing/removal\n- [ ] Implement volume creation\n- [ ] Implement volume listing/removal\n\n## Phase 5: Error Handling & Testing\n- [ ] Implement retry logic\n- [ ] Add comprehensive error handling\n- [ ] Write unit tests with mocks\n- [ ] Write integration tests\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/plan.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/plan.md","time":{"start":1775894354739,"end":1775894354766}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894354769,"sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8cb806001dZdtSNWay3sdRi","messageID":"msg_d7b8c2a50001BFxiORKBoKqeCK","sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:13","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/tasks.md","content":"# AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Task Breakdown\n\n## T1: Service Structure\n- Create `cmd/cli/internal/docker_service.py`\n- Define DockerService class with initialization\n- Implement backend detection (SDK vs CLI)\n- Create configuration dataclass\n\n## T2: Exception Hierarchy\n- Create `cmd/cli/internal/docker_exceptions.py`\n- Define base DockerError class\n- Create specific exceptions (ConnectionError, NotFoundError, etc.)\n\n## T3: Container Lifecycle\n- Implement `create_container()` method\n- Implement `start_container()` method\n- Implement `stop_container()` method\n- Implement `remove_container()` method\n- Implement `list_containers()` method\n- Implement `inspect_container()` method\n\n## T4: Image Management\n- Implement `pull_image()` with progress\n- Implement `build_image()` with build args\n- Implement `list_images()` method\n- Implement `remove_image()` method\n\n## T5: Network & Volume\n- Implement network CRUD operations\n- Implement volume CRUD operations\n\n## T6: Testing\n- Write unit tests with mocked backends\n- Create integration tests with real Docker\n- Add test fixtures for containers/images\n\n## Dependencies\n- Blocked by: None\n- Related to: AR-023 (K8sProvider)\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/tasks.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/tasks.md","time":{"start":1775894354742,"end":1775894354768}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894354771,"sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8cdc5f001c1xBOML64GQW5v","messageID":"msg_d7b8c2a50001BFxiORKBoKqeCK","sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:14","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md","content":"# AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Delta Spec\n\n## Overview\nThis document describes the delta specification for implementing the DockerService\nencapsulation layer in the cmd/cli module.\n\n## Current State\n- Docker operations scattered in various places\n- No unified abstraction for container management\n- Direct subprocess calls to docker CLI in some places\n- Limited error handling for Docker operations\n\n## Target State\nA unified DockerService class that:\n- Provides clean abstraction over Docker operations\n- Supports both Docker SDK and CLI fallback\n- Offers comprehensive error handling\n- Returns structured data\n- Supports async operations\n\n## Delta Analysis\n\n### New Components\n1. **DockerService** (`cmd/cli/internal/docker_service.py`)\n   - Main service class with all Docker operations\n   - Backend selection (SDK/CLI)\n   - Connection management\n\n2. **Docker Exceptions** (`cmd/cli/internal/docker_exceptions.py`)\n   - DockerError base class\n   - ConnectionError, ImageNotFoundError, etc.\n\n3. **Configuration** (`cmd/cli/internal/docker_config.py`)\n   - DockerConnectionConfig dataclass\n   - Environment variable parsing\n\n### Modified Components\n- None (this is a new service layer)\n\n### Dependencies\n- docker-py library (optional, for SDK backend)\n- Existing subprocess utilities for CLI backend\n\n## Interface Specification\n\n### DockerService Class\n```python\nclass DockerService:\n    def __init__(self, config: DockerConfig = None)\n    def create_container(self, image: str, **kwargs) -> Container\n    def start_container(self, container_id: str) -> None\n    def stop_container(self, container_id: str, timeout: int = 30) -> None\n    def remove_container(self, container_id: str, force: bool = False) -> None\n    def list_containers(self, all: bool = False) -> List[Container]\n    def pull_image(self, image: str, callback: Callable = None) -> Image\n    def build_image(self, path: str, tag: str, **kwargs) -> Image\n    def list_images(self) -> List[Image]\n    def remove_image(self, image_id: str, force: bool = False) -> None\n```\n\n## Implementation Notes\n- Prefer Docker SDK when available\n- Fallback to CLI for operations not supported by SDK\n- All methods should accept timeout parameter\n- Progress callbacks for long operations\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/delta-spec.md","time":{"start":1775894354746,"end":1775894354769}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894354773,"sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8d1a89001Htt68VmDTegn1r","messageID":"msg_d7b8c2a50001BFxiORKBoKqeCK","sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:15","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/tests.md","content":"# AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Test Specification\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n### Service Initialization Tests\n- `test_initializes_with_sdk_backend`: Uses docker-py when available\n- `test_falls_back_to_cli_backend`: Falls back to CLI when SDK unavailable\n- `test_raises_on_no_backend`: Error when neither backend available\n- `test_loads_config_from_env`: Config from environment variables\n\n### Container Operation Tests\n- `test_create_container_calls_sdk`: SDK backend create path\n- `test_create_container_calls_cli`: CLI backend create path\n- `test_start_container_success`: Container start happy path\n- `test_stop_container_with_timeout`: Stop with custom timeout\n- `test_remove_container_force`: Force removal\n- `test_list_containers_returns_structure`: Proper data structure\n- `test_inspect_container_parses_json`: JSON parsing for CLI backend\n\n### Image Operation Tests\n- `test_pull_image_with_callback`: Progress callback invoked\n- `test_pull_image_raises_on_failure`: Error handling\n- `test_build_image_with_args`: Build args passed correctly\n- `test_list_images_returns_list`: Returns image list\n- `test_remove_image_force`: Force image removal\n\n### Error Handling Tests\n- `test_connection_error_raised`: Connection failures\n- `test_not_found_error_raised`: 404 scenarios\n- `test_timeout_error_raised`: Operation timeouts\n- `test_retry_on_transient_error`: Retry logic\n\n## Integration Tests\n\n### Happy Path\n- `test_full_container_lifecycle`: Create → Start → Stop → Remove\n- `test_pull_and_run`: Pull image and run container\n- `test_build_and_run`: Build image and run container\n\n### Error Scenarios\n- `test_invalid_image_name`: Invalid image handling\n- `test_port_conflict`: Port already in use\n- `test_volume_not_found`: Missing volume\n\n## Test Data\n- Mock Docker SDK client\n- Mock subprocess for CLI backend\n- Sample Dockerfile for build tests\n- Test container fixtures\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/tests.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/tests.md","time":{"start":1775894354749,"end":1775894354772}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894354775,"sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8d47380012CwC5kBACFqxHT","messageID":"msg_d7b8c2a50001BFxiORKBoKqeCK","sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:16","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/notes.md","content":"# AR-024: DockerService 封装 — Notes\n\n## Status\nInitialized: 2026-04-11\n\n## Open Questions\n- Should we enforce minimum Docker API version?\n- How to handle Docker Compose scenarios?\n- Should we support podman as alternative backend?\n- What logging level is appropriate for Docker operations?\n\n## References\n- See AR-023 for K8sProvider implementation patterns\n- Related to container deployment architecture\n- Check existing docker_service.py for any reusable code\n\n## Change Log\n- 2026-04-11: Initial scaffold created\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/notes.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/notes.md","time":{"start":1775894354752,"end":1775894354774}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775894355142,"sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","part":{"id":"prt_d7b8c33ba001R6ZlLhl9ojxAcx","messageID":"msg_d7b8c2a50001BFxiORKBoKqeCK","sessionID":"ses_284747457ffeiwSMHZcOFUQyO2","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:10","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml","content":"id: AR-024\ntitle: DockerService 封装\nmodule: cmd/cli\nlanguage: Python\nsize: M\nstatus: open\n\n# AR-024: DockerService 封装\n# Module: cmd/cli\n# Language: Python\n# Size: M\n\n# OpenSpec Metadata\nopenspec:\n  version: \"1.0\"\n  project: agentcube\n\n# Architecture Requirement\nrequirement:\n  type: service-layer\n  description: |\n    Encapsulate Docker operations into a DockerService class within the cmd/cli module.\n    This service will provide a clean, testable abstraction over Docker CLI commands\n    and Docker SDK for Python, supporting container lifecycle management, image\n    operations, and network/volume management for agent deployment.\n\n# Scope\nscope:\n  in:\n    - DockerService class implementation\n    - Container lifecycle operations (create, start, stop, remove)\n    - Image management (pull, build, list, remove)\n    - Network operations (create, list, remove)\n    - Volume management (create, list, remove)\n    - Error handling and retry logic\n    - Configuration management for Docker connection\n  out:\n    - Kubernetes service implementation (AR-023)\n    - Container registry backend\n    - Multi-node Docker Swarm support\n    - Web UI for container management\n\n# Acceptance Criteria\nacceptance:\n  - DockerService provides clean API for all Docker operations\n  - Supports both Docker CLI fallback and Docker SDK\n  - Handles connection errors gracefully\n  - Provides detailed error messages\n  - Supports async/await pattern for long-running operations\n  - Returns structured data for all operations\n  - Unit testable with mock interfaces\n\n# References\nreferences:\n  - https://docker-py.readthedocs.io/\n  - https://docs.docker.com/engine/api/\n\n# Estimation\nestimation:\n  size: M\n  story_points: 5\n  days: 3\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-022/spec.yaml":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml":[]},"filepath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/changes/AR-024/spec.yaml","time":{"start":1775894354730,"end":1775894355139}}}}
